  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"primary\"\u003e\n\t\t\u003cmain id=\"main\" role=\"main\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003carticle id=\"post-34903\"\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\u003cp\u003eI have a Christmas cookie recipe for you today. Chinese Almond Cookies are delish and easy to make, plus since they bake up flat, they can be easily stacked in a bag or box, making them easy to give for Christmas gift giving.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"680\" height=\"1020\" src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Recipe-for-Chinese-Almond-Cookies.jpg\" alt=\"Chinese Almond Cookie Recipe\" srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Recipe-for-Chinese-Almond-Cookies.jpg 680w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Recipe-for-Chinese-Almond-Cookies-200x300.jpg 200w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Recipe-for-Chinese-Almond-Cookies-180x270.jpg 180w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Recipe-for-Chinese-Almond-Cookies-300x450.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" data-pin-description=\"Chinese almond cookies are perfect for Christmas gift giving because they bake up flat and perfect for stacking in boxes for gift giving.\" data-pin-media=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Recipe-for-Chinese-Almond-Cookies.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20width=\u0026#39;680\u0026#39;%20height=\u0026#39;1020\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20680%201020\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Recipe-for-Chinese-Almond-Cookies.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Recipe-for-Chinese-Almond-Cookies.jpg 680w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Recipe-for-Chinese-Almond-Cookies-200x300.jpg 200w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Recipe-for-Chinese-Almond-Cookies-180x270.jpg 180w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Recipe-for-Chinese-Almond-Cookies-300x450.jpg 300w\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAround this time every year I search for new Christmas cookies to make and give. Over the past 10 + years I have been going to an annual holiday cookie exchange that my friend hosts. One winner was \u003ca href=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/2012/12/pecan-cherry-dunking-cookie-recipe.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003ePecan Cherry Cookies.\u003c/a\u003e  Another were what I called \u003ca href=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/easiest-cookies-i-ever-made.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003eThe Easiest Christmas Cookies I Ever Made. \u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eI always try to make something with a wow factor, but I find my efforts never turn out or look as good as the photo in the magazine or cookbook shows.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-how-to-make-chinese-almond-cookies\"\u003eHow to Make Chinese Almond Cookies\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"680\" height=\"1020\" src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Kitchen-Aid-Stand-Mixer-1-of-1.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen Aid Mixer whipping up Chinese Almond Cookies\" srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Kitchen-Aid-Stand-Mixer-1-of-1.jpg 680w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Kitchen-Aid-Stand-Mixer-1-of-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Kitchen-Aid-Stand-Mixer-1-of-1-180x270.jpg 180w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Kitchen-Aid-Stand-Mixer-1-of-1-300x450.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" data-pin-title=\"Christmas Baking Ideas\" data-pin-description=\"Christmas cookie and treats from the oven. \" data-pin-media=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Kitchen-Aid-Stand-Mixer-1-of-1.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20width=\u0026#39;680\u0026#39;%20height=\u0026#39;1020\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20680%201020\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Kitchen-Aid-Stand-Mixer-1-of-1.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Kitchen-Aid-Stand-Mixer-1-of-1.jpg 680w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Kitchen-Aid-Stand-Mixer-1-of-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Kitchen-Aid-Stand-Mixer-1-of-1-180x270.jpg 180w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Kitchen-Aid-Stand-Mixer-1-of-1-300x450.jpg 300w\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eOver the years, I found the best cookies and the tastiest are always the simplest ones to make. They are the ones everyone grabs.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eI am sharing one of those cookie recipes with you today…one of my faves… Chinese Almond Cookies.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"680\" height=\"1020\" src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/more-cookie-baking-tips.jpg\" alt=\"Cookie Baking tips making Chinese Almond Cookies\" srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/more-cookie-baking-tips.jpg 680w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/more-cookie-baking-tips-200x300.jpg 200w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/more-cookie-baking-tips-180x270.jpg 180w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/more-cookie-baking-tips-300x450.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" data-pin-media=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/more-cookie-baking-tips.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20width=\u0026#39;680\u0026#39;%20height=\u0026#39;1020\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20680%201020\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/more-cookie-baking-tips.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/more-cookie-baking-tips.jpg 680w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/more-cookie-baking-tips-200x300.jpg 200w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/more-cookie-baking-tips-180x270.jpg 180w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/more-cookie-baking-tips-300x450.jpg 300w\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you like almonds, you will love these cookies, if you love easy… ditto!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"680\" height=\"1020\" src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Cookie-baking-tips.jpg\" alt=\"Cookies to make for Christmas\" srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Cookie-baking-tips.jpg 680w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Cookie-baking-tips-200x300.jpg 200w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Cookie-baking-tips-180x270.jpg 180w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Cookie-baking-tips-300x450.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" data-pin-media=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Cookie-baking-tips.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20width=\u0026#39;680\u0026#39;%20height=\u0026#39;1020\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20680%201020\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Cookie-baking-tips.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Cookie-baking-tips.jpg 680w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Cookie-baking-tips-200x300.jpg 200w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Cookie-baking-tips-180x270.jpg 180w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Cookie-baking-tips-300x450.jpg 300w\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThere is a surprise ingredient in them – you have the option to use water, gin or vodka. I have tried each and think when I make them with gin they taste the best.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/How-to-add-sugar-to-cookies.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"680\" height=\"1020\" src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/How-to-add-sugar-to-cookies.jpg\" alt=\"Christmas cookie baking idea\" srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/How-to-add-sugar-to-cookies.jpg 680w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/How-to-add-sugar-to-cookies-200x300.jpg 200w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/How-to-add-sugar-to-cookies-180x270.jpg 180w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/How-to-add-sugar-to-cookies-300x450.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" data-pin-media=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/How-to-add-sugar-to-cookies.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20width=\u0026#39;680\u0026#39;%20height=\u0026#39;1020\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20680%201020\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/How-to-add-sugar-to-cookies.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/How-to-add-sugar-to-cookies.jpg 680w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/How-to-add-sugar-to-cookies-200x300.jpg 200w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/How-to-add-sugar-to-cookies-180x270.jpg 180w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/How-to-add-sugar-to-cookies-300x450.jpg 300w\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eI like sprinkling them with sanding sugar, but you can simply place an almond on the center of each cookie before baking.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"680\" height=\"453\" src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinesse-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-with-vodka.jpg\" alt=\"Cookie baking tips\" srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinesse-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-with-vodka.jpg 680w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinesse-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-with-vodka-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" data-pin-media=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinesse-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-with-vodka.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20width=\u0026#39;680\u0026#39;%20height=\u0026#39;453\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20680%20453\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinesse-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-with-vodka.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinesse-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-with-vodka.jpg 680w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinesse-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-with-vodka-300x200.jpg 300w\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Kitchen-Aid-Stand-Mixer-1-of-1.jpg\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/a\u003eIn under 10 minutes, they are done and ready for consumption.\u003ca href=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Kitchen-Aid-Mixr-.jpg\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"680\" height=\"1020\" src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinese-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-that-has-gin-in-it.jpg\" alt=\"Chinese Almond Cookie Recipe\" srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinese-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-that-has-gin-in-it.jpg 680w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinese-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-that-has-gin-in-it-200x300.jpg 200w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinese-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-that-has-gin-in-it-180x270.jpg 180w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinese-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-that-has-gin-in-it-300x450.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" data-pin-media=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinese-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-that-has-gin-in-it.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20width=\u0026#39;680\u0026#39;%20height=\u0026#39;1020\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20680%201020\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinese-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-that-has-gin-in-it.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinese-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-that-has-gin-in-it.jpg 680w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinese-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-that-has-gin-in-it-200x300.jpg 200w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinese-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-that-has-gin-in-it-180x270.jpg 180w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Chinese-Almond-Cookie-Recipe-that-has-gin-in-it-300x450.jpg 300w\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Kitchen-Aid-Stand-Mixer.jpg\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/a\u003eBe prepared for a few to disappear before they have even cooled.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-cookies-make-great-holiday-hostess-gifts\"\u003eCookies Make Great Holiday Hostess Gifts\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePlace them in a gift wrapped box to keep them from getting crushed and then give them as hostess gifts this holiday season.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePlace them in a gift wrapped box to keep them from getting crushed and then give them as hostess gifts this holiday season.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIf you don’t have a box to use, check your pantry for empty plastic-wrap or foil boxes. Their long, thin shape is perfect for holding a batch of cookies.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSimply glue gift wrap to the cardboard and line the inside with tissue paper. Add a bow and you have one very affordable and pretty gift.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-45833\" data-recipe-id=\"45833\" data-servings=\"0\"\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eChinese Almond Cookie Recipe\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"45833\" data-servings=\"0\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1/2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ewhole almonds\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003esifted flour\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1/2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etsp.\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/clabber-girl-gluten-free-double-acting-baking-powder-8-1oz/-/A-14770673?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ebaking powder\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1/4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etsp.\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/iodized-salt-26oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-78140513?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003esalt\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1/2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ebutter or margarine\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1/3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/granulated-sugar-4lbs-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-78471310?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003esugar\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1/2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etsp.\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/mccormick-pure-almond-extract-2oz/-/A-53245136?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ealmond extract\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eTbs.\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003egin\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003evodka, or water\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSanding sugar or sprinkles\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"45833\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-45833-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eFinely chop or grind almonds.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-45833-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eThoroughly cream butter and sugar.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-45833-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eStir flour with baking powder and salt and add to creamed mixture.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-45833-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eStir in remaining ingredients.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-45833-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eForm dough into small balls on a greased or parchment lined cookie sheet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-45833-step-0-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePress with a back of a large spoon to flatten each ball\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-45833-step-0-6\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eSprinkle with white or colored sanding sugar or sprinkles.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-45833-step-0-7\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eBake at 350 for 15 minutes or until very lightly golden.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eLooking for more holiday hostess or a food gift ideas? \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/hostess-gift-garlic-pretzels.html\"\u003eThese aren’t cookies\u003c/a\u003e, but readers rave about them.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eOr try my other fave\u003ca href=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/pecan-cherry-dunking-cookie-recipe.html\"\u003e Christmas Cookie recipe.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" data-pin-description=\"Discover how to create the most scrumptious Christmas cookie that\u0026#39;s super easy to whip up and perfect for stacking in cookie boxes! These irresistible almond cookies will make your cookie box the star of the gift giving season!\" data-pin-title=\"Christmas Cookie Recipes Easy\" src=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Christmas-cookie-recipe-easy-683x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Christmas cookie recipe for almond cookies\" srcset=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Christmas-cookie-recipe-easy-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Christmas-cookie-recipe-easy-200x300.jpg 200w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Christmas-cookie-recipe-easy-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Christmas-cookie-recipe-easy.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" data-pin-media=\"https://inmyownstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Chr